00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:16,160
once a person dies, they die for good.

293
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,360
The Chen Huo'e from back then

294
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,280
may not be the same as the one of today.

295
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,080
Lord Shen,

296
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,200
since you are unwell,

297
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,800
there's no need to force yourself.

298
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:35,520
It's a mere scratch,

299
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:36,880
and it's already healed.

300
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,280
Alright.

301
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:44,120
Since Lady Xu is vouching for you,

302
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,760
then the case

303
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:50,080
will be assigned to the IG.

304
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:51,360
Yes, ma'am.

305
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,440
Then,

306
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,520
the Imperial Academy

307
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:59,120
should be handled by Lord Zhang.

308
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,520
He is a civil official.

309
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:02,360
It would be easier for him to communicate

310
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:03,720
with students.

311
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,720
Lord Shen.

312
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:10,280
How about you take charge of the security

313
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,240
of the capital region?

314
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,280
Your Royal Highness,

315
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,920
this is a matter of vital importance.

316
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:16,840
Nothing could go wrong.

317
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,320
The IG lacks manpower

318
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:20,000
for full coverage.

319
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,240
How cunning you are!

320
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:25,280
You often lament a lack of power.

321
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,800
But today,

322
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,160
you are making excuses.

323
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,200
Do you believe I don't know

324
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,960
