325
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:36,280
I wouldn't dare.

326
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,240
Wouldn't dare?

327
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:40,120
I see that you two are scheming.

328
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:43,000
You are both quite bold.

329
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,680
Apologies, Your Royal Highness.

330
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:47,400
Alright, alright.

331
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:51,320
As I entrust you with the security,

332
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:52,560
you will be given the authority to

333
00:16:52,560 --> 00:16:54,560
mobilize resources from offices.

334
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,920
During the Academy examination,

335
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,960
any matters related to security

336
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,520
will be under

337
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:03,000
your coordination.

338
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:06,600
Gratitude, Your Royal Highness.

339
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:17,320
Your Highness!

340
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:19,680
Mr Zhang has secured the academy's task.

341
00:17:21,120 --> 00:17:21,920
That old bastard!

342
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,240
He has gotten ahead again.

343
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:33,840
Now, this is getting interesting.

344
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:41,600
Your Highness.

345
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:43,159
Sir.

346
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,159
You came in time.

347
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:46,280
Take a look at my yellow peony.

348
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:47,159
Isn't it blooming beautifully?

349
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:48,840
Good.

350
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,000
[Your Highness.]

351
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,400
[Her Royal Highness]

352
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:54,240
has already entrusted

353
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,720
the examination to me.

354
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:57,240
[The students of the Imperial Academy]

355
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,920
[are the best among scholars in the realm.]

356
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:00,560
If the examination succeeded,

357
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:01,640
[you would be]

358
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:03,080
[be even more advantageous]

359
00:18:03,120 --> 00:18:05,040
to secure the position of regent.

360
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,080
Sir,

361
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,040
whether Princess Ying

362
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:09,880
or I become the regent,

363
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:10,680
we are all here to

364
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:12,640
serve Her Highness and His Majesty.

365
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,400
That is not correct.

366
00:18:15,720 --> 00:18:16,720
His Majesty suffers from delayed speech.

367
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:18,280
Her Highness is in her twilight years.

368
00:18:18,320 --> 00:18:19,040
The regent is of utmost importance

369
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:21,160
to the foundation of the empire.

370
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:22,440
On this matter,

371
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:25,120
You must not be negligent.

372
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:28,080
I appreciate your dedication.

373
00:18:28,560 --> 00:18:30,240
Please clear up misunderstandings,

374
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:32,080
and show love

375
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:32,720
and respect to

376
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,520
students from humble backgrounds.

377
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:39,640
Yes.

378
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:40,680
Of course.

379
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:41,440
However,

380
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:43,240
Shen Du has been tasked with

381
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:44,560
the responsibility for the capital's security,

382
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:46,480
which gives him more power.

383
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:51,160
He is indeed capable.

384
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:52,720
No matter what situation

385
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:54,360
he encounters or trouble

386
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:56,040
he faces,

387
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:59,000
he always finds a way to handle it.

388
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:00,840
Sir,

389
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:02,960
don't you think so?

390
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:05,920
I agree.

391
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:07,760
Now that he's

392
00:19:07,760 --> 00:19:09,360
taken on the security task,

393
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:10,680
[should the situation]

394
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:11,400
[in Xiang'an be a bit]

395
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:13,400
[more chaotic?]

396
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,960
Your Highness,

397
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:17,800
should we "help" him a bit?

398
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:22,800
I beg your pardon, sir?

399
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,080
You may excuse yourself now.

400
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:54,360
[Sir,]

401
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,120
[the task of overseeing the examination]

402
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:57,600
[has ultimately been given to the PM.]

403
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,920
Her Highness has entrusted the security

404
00:19:58,920 --> 00:19:59,760
of the capital region to us.

405
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:00,880
Is this meant to be a consolation?

406
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,800
This is exactly the outcome I desired.

407
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,120
You don't seem disappointed.

408
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:07,800
A gust of wind is coming.

409
00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:10,520
During the examination,

410
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,200
Princess Ying, Prince Xian,

411
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,360
the PM and Lai Luozhi

412
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,840
will surely take action.

413
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:15,880
Keep a close watch.

414
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:16,840
Understood.

415
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:18,960
The security around the academy

416
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:19,920
must not be underestimated.

417
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:20,640
We can mobilize palace guards

418
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,240
and inspectors for assistance.

419
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:24,960
And the security of all the imperial

420
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,080
offices is the same.

421
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:29,760
Keep our men there,

422
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,120
especially

423
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:33,960
the Imperial Secretariat.

424
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:36,120
Yes, sir.

425
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:12,360
Who is it?

426
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,840
Lord Commander!

427
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,360
Thank you for the gifts you sent to

428
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:29,880
my family.

429
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:31,040
They all loved them a lot.

430
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:34,000
Not worth mentioning.

431
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:39,200
Anything interesting happened

432
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,000
during the assembly today?

433
00:21:41,840 --> 00:21:42,680
Not much.

434
00:21:43,320 --> 00:21:44,200
Lai Luozhi requested to take over

435
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:46,120
the investigation of the Chen Huo'e case.

436
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:48,640
Did Her Royal Highness give it to him?

437
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:57,840
She gave it to me.

438
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:58,880
Hey...

439
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:05,400
Are you saying that the case

440
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:07,000
will still be handled by the IG?

441
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:09,640
Bravo!

442
00:22:20,360 --> 00:22:21,560
I'll go prepare ink for you.

443
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:20,200
No matter how you tidy up a puppy house,

444
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,720
it will still be a puppy house.

445
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:47,840
Is your hand

446
00:23:50,280 --> 00:23:51,320
better?

447
00:23:57,080 --> 00:23:58,240
I was bitten by a puppy.

448
00:23:58,960 --> 00:24:00,200
It won't heal that fast.

449
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:23,080
Lord Commander.

450
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:26,280
Please read the case files a little.

451
00:24:26,280 --> 00:24:27,400
Rest for a bit.

452
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:29,400
How about I cook for you?

453
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:30,880
You know how to cook?

454
00:24:31,320 --> 00:24:32,440
Don't underestimate me.

455
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:34,880
I am the renowned Lady Yan Xing.

456
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:38,920
Yeah, right.

457
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:40,760
"She has extraordinary talents,"

458
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:45,120
"proficient in writing, painting, embroidery,"

459
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:48,040
"and classics, and wealthy in knowledge."

460
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,800
"Her reputation as a virtuous lady"

461
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:52,720
"is unmatched in Xiang'an."

462
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:14,280
[Let's go.]

463
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:16,840
Come on.

464
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:29,760
Please sit.

465
00:25:36,720 --> 00:25:37,520
Sir,

466
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:39,280
I made these myself.

467
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:40,160
Give it a try.

468
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:53,560
Try this chicken.

469
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,280
How is it?

470
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:13,680
Surprisingly,

471
00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:18,680
it's not bad.

472
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:23,480
See?

473
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:24,760
I told you so.

474
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:26,480
Cooking and autopsy

475
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:27,680
have similar principles.

476
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,160
Using preservation

477
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:30,600
and dissecting methods

478
00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:31,720
to handle this chicken,

479
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:32,640
the taste will be

480
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,600
just like that of a freshly killed one.

481
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,280
Yeah,

482
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:50,480
Now, try this soup.

483
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,840
The inspiration for using this spice

484
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:13,480
comes from the spices used by

485
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:15,560
Lady Tang for preserving corpses.

486
00:27:16,600 --> 00:27:17,400
Smell it.

487
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:18,720
Isn't the aroma delightful?

488
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,520
Isn't it?

489
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:20,520
Very fragrant, right?

490
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:47,520
Is there something you want?

491
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:51,920
Just say it.

492
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:56,360
That fast, really?

493
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:04,800
Well,

494
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,880
can I participate in

495
00:28:10,560 --> 00:28:11,720
the case?

496
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,520
No, you cannot.

497
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:15,720
Can't you see

498
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,280
how complicated this case is?

499
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:19,320
The Ministry of Justice and the Supreme Court

500
00:28:19,320 --> 00:28:20,400
are both trying to avoid it.

501
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,480
And you come begging to be part of it?

502
00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:23,360
I understand.

503
00:28:24,120 --> 00:28:25,640
Lai Luozhi and Princess Ying

504
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,080
both came to see me today.

505
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:28,360
In both open and hidden ways,

506
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:29,120
they just don't want me

507
00:28:29,120 --> 00:28:30,360
to get involved in this case.

508
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:31,840
But I am just a

509
00:28:31,840 --> 00:28:32,960
lowly clerk.

510
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:34,640
Could they really be wary of me?

511
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:36,280
What they are wary of is just

512
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,360
my title of "Lord Commander's wife."

513
00:28:42,840 --> 00:28:44,080
if you are aware of all this...

514
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:46,720
You have already taken on this case,

515
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:48,040
and I am now, without a doubt,

516
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:49,520
the genuine and rightful

517
00:28:49,520 --> 00:28:50,280
Lord Commander's wife.

518
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,840
How could I possibly

519
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:53,080
escape from all this?

520
00:28:53,080 --> 00:28:54,560
If you encounter danger,

521
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:56,320
how could I possibly remain unscathed?

522
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,520
Forgive me.

523
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:10,720
What is there to forgive?

524
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:12,600
Finding the truth

525
00:29:12,600 --> 00:29:13,520
and clearing one's name

526
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:15,080
has always been my ideal.

527
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:18,800
I only ask

528
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:19,480
that you give me

529
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:20,560
the authority to investigate.

530
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:24,600
Rest assured,

531
00:29:24,600 --> 00:29:26,160
I will definitely not hold you back.

532
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,800
I won't be a burden to you either.

533
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:50,680
But you must promise me

534
00:29:51,040 --> 00:29:51,800
that during the investigation,

535
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:52,920
if anything happens,

536
00:29:53,280 --> 00:29:54,200
you will discuss it with me first

537
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:55,120
before making any decisions.

538
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:56,560
You must not act on your own.

539
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:57,320
Of course.

540
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:58,880
You are Lord Commander,

541
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,200
my superior,

542
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,920
so I will definitely follow your command.

543
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,440
Henceforth, my allegiance

544
00:30:04,440 --> 00:30:06,160
lies solely with my Lord Commander.

545
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:06,880
Is this to your liking?

546
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,040
Silly.

547
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:47,080
Imperial Guard on duty.

548
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:26,520
Is Lord Chen Shoujie here?

549
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,280
I am Yan Xing, from the Ministry of Justice.

550
00:31:28,280 --> 00:31:29,960
I have a few questions to ask him.

551
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:35,960
That night, my lady was in a good mood,

552
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,160
cooking herself.

553
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:39,000
She made mutton and smoked chicken.

554
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:40,840
She also baked flatbreads and stuffed breads.

555
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:42,760
[She even rewarded me with a bowl of wine.]

556
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:44,000
[I slept until midnight,]

557
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:44,880
[when I suddenly]

558
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:45,960
[heard crying.]

559
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:46,640
[Darling!]

560
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,480
In the end, Her Lady...

561
00:32:37,320 --> 00:32:38,280
Officer,

562
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:39,720
be careful.

563
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:52,240
My Lord!

564
00:32:53,760 --> 00:32:54,480
- My Lord!
- Fire!

565
00:32:54,480 --> 00:32:55,680
My Lord!

566
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:56,480
Fire!

567
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:57,120
My Lord!

568
00:32:57,120 --> 00:32:57,960
- My Lord!
- Moth! (Chen Huo'e's last character)

569
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,200
- There's a fire!
- My Lord!

570
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:00,480
- There's a fire!
- My Lord!

571
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,640
Moth! Moth!

572
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:04,880
Is he talking about Chen Huo'e?

573
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:35,520
Keep distance from the rest of us.

574
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,360
From now on, you just sit...

575
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:43,720
Here.

576
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,920
Since you are working for Imperial Guard,

577
00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:06,600
then you have nothing to do with

578
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:07,800
the Ministry of Justice.

579
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:11,200
No matter what trouble you cause,

580
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:13,640
it has nothing to do with us.

581
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,440
The Ministry of Justice

582
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,920
will stay out of this case.

583
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:21,680
Stay out!

584
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:36,800
